headline: FICO Educational Analytics Challenge Program Continues its Third Year, Empowering Students with Hands-On Experience Building Responsible AI Models
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., February 02, 2026--FICO today announced the continuation of its FICO® Educational Analytics Challenge for the Spring 2026 semester.
